item.title: About Me
item.content:encoded:
Hi, I'm Jamie Gray. I'm a UX / UI Designer.

I am looking for the opportunity to connect with motivated teams, to learn from others, and help build software tools to improve people's lives.

Passionate about efficiency, process optimization, and building things at the intersection of humanities and technology. 

Current:

Working full-time at an engineering firm (view on LinkedIn) until a door opens up in the tech world. 

Previous:

I spent a full year after graduating high school freelancing as a professional filmmaker; documenting humanitarian efforts in Iraq, shooting wedding videos, and up on stage with some of my favorite bands.
